Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:53.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,450)\3c&HE4772B&\blur1.5}将那无论承载多少梦想 绝无虚伪的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:56.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)\3c&HB1601B&\blur1.5}Ah… Oh 一直做我自己
